tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
I have got very good consultation, I feel the doctor is giving correct treatment and effective medicines. He coolly listens to the complaint examines child properly, . 
Also is very much available on the phone for out of clinic hours if some problem is there. 
He is very reasonable with regards to consultation fees. 

I strongly recommend this paediatrician.
reply_text:
Hello. 
 Thank u for your kind words. You are my regular old patient. It was a surprise feedback for me realy  unexpected. What I have observed regarding feedback that I have received feedback from new patients, patients coming from practo booking etc. Old patients  feedback is little special as we  get attached with our old patients like a family. Thank u again for taking out valuable time to say few words about me.
Regards

review: Very friendly doctor. Best part is he listens to your queries and concerns and then provide expert guidance point by point. I would highly recommend doc Thamke.

review: It's been more than 3 years I have been visiting Thamke sir for my child. His friendliness, proper attention to the child's problem and accuracy in treatment makes worth the visit, all the way from Ulhasnagar. Thank you sir for my child's excellent health.
reply_text:
Thank you for your kind words. Tanay is sweet boy and you both are a good parents. I have seen Tanay growing in front of me and I appreciate your trust in me in this year. I appreciate and thank you. You  travel all the way from Ulhasnagar  I am sorry for your inconvenience. Take care and thank you again for writing few good words for me. It really encourages me to do good work for small innocent growing citizens of our great nation. 
Regards.
